{"tid":2045185,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"91年金像獎，女主角鄭裕玲(表姐你好嘢)拎而唔係劉嘉玲(阿飛正傳)仲有無咩背後故事？","createTime":"2020-05-31T15:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T13:40:21.000Z","uid":7439,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"77f72528a02320505d6ebfff9db626c82fb8094a","tid":2045185,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T15:29:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_ABgAQHBhSk?t=3877\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_ABgAQHBhSk%3Ft%3D3877&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGkZZ0ArqIWVBMBEeODt8eII%3D&h=5a981211\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_ABgAQHBhSk?t=3877</a><br />\n<blockquote>第10屆香港電影金像獎 最佳女主角<br />\n<br />\n張艾嘉《廟街皇后》<br />\n張曼玉《愛在別鄉的季節》<br />\n鞏俐《秦俑》<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">鄭裕玲《表姐，你好嘢！》（由陳自強、張堅庭代領）</span><br />\n劉嘉玲《阿飛正傳》<br />\n<br />\n頒獎嘉賓：周潤發、林青霞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<em>劉嘉玲憶起往事，她說「《阿飛正傳》我是輸給鄭裕玲的（《表姐，妳好嘢》），因為她們４個人都沒來，因為她們都覺得她們會輸，然後我去了，結果不是我，就是你有一種感覺是這個不是事實吧，那個時候幾本雜誌的封面，都已經提早幫我拍完照，他們都覺得怎麼可能不是妳。因為我在法國都拿完獎了，結果揭開來不是我，我是會有一點接受不了。但是我在法國南特，已經拿到最佳女主角，所以我覺得我沒有失禮，我交了我的功課，只是你香港這個社會可能，電影這個圈子評審，我得不到你們的認同而已。」</em><br />\n<br />\n<em>林青霞是頒獎嘉賓，她跟我說，假如看見名單上是我的名字會馬上給我遞眼色。信封一拆，她果然向我遞眼色，我已經準備站起來，不料卻是鄭裕玲，而不是劉嘉玲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></em><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gzQpsLV5_0s?t=1600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgzQpsLV5_0s%3Ft%3D1600&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGkZZ0ArqIWVBMBEeODt8eII%3D&h=a0b3810c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gzQpsLV5_0s?t=1600</a>"},{"pid":"1eefeb1359498b7fadb225017e768cf3c5ae74c6","tid":2045185,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T15:30:11.000Z","msg":"<em>【表姐你好嘢】90年代的「大家都係中國人」｜九龍霸王電影彈．鄭立<br />\n<br />\n九十年代的看法，並不是那種甘願受現在的「中國」統治的大中華主義，反而是用自稱中國，來要求對方尊重自己的身份和意見。<br />\n<br />\n可是這只是一個美麗的誤會，這二十年間，大家才醒覺到一件事：自稱中國人，並不會得到其他自稱中國人的人的尊重與愛護，中華大一統論只是包裝過的帝國主義。<br />\n<br />\n然後你就開始明白，為何朝鮮、日本、越南，都曾經自稱「中華」，繼承中華文明，但最後都放棄了這件事，開始追求新的身份認同。</em>"},{"pid":"b2625e0ac5b3246d446c890787fe4669042a5d76","tid":2045185,"uid":7439,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T15:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/44708873_260082414703328_8673043824085303296_o.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_sid=2d5d41&amp;_nc_ohc=EgcC_gOp87AAX9FNC8w&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=13a442cb54bf8774c1add99a1205cfa2&amp;oe=5EF92EAE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F44708873_260082414703328_8673043824085303296_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26_nc_sid%3D2d5d41%26_nc_ohc%3DEgcC_gOp87AAX9FNC8w%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3D13a442cb54bf8774c1add99a1205cfa2%26oe%3D5EF92EAE&h=ef5fab84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>話比你聽吖，民主唔係賜予，係要爭取嘅，不過咁，我哋個黨好寬大嘅，你哋唔需要爭取，我哋係會俾你嘅，你要幾多，話我聽呀，我地俾你。</em>"},{"pid":"8d35f1a12495252e225fc55b2b86e99482536997","tid":2045185,"uid":7439,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T15:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2d4MQcwJgwcIsLsGBGutMT1LGdw=/802x625/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LCNWCJ4RQLDEAI2R2ONSACOCGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2d4MQcwJgwcIsLsGBGutMT1LGdw%3D%2F802x625%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLCNWCJ4RQLDEAI2R2ONSACOCGA.jpg&h=fe3c1d8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e868a1f7689873eb9c76e286ddda09147d7ce3","tid":2045185,"uid":167289,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T15:34:12.000Z","msg":"做戲渣囉<br />\n套戲記得張曼玉都唔記得劉嘉玲啦"},{"pid":"e9eebf3f5aa83b2c222790acfe3e5c7c9ca2debf","tid":2045185,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T15:34:13.000Z","msg":"你为什么不讲普通话？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji